commit.message:
perf: add pagination to notes/bookmarks/todos/learningNotes

Backend (4 routers):
- notes.list: add limit/offset/type params, return {items, hasMore}
- bookmarks.list: add limit/offset, return {items, hasMore}
- todos.list: add limit/offset, return {items, hasMore}
- learningNotebook.listNotes: add limit/offset, return {items, hasMore}

Frontend:
- notes-page-client: full rewrite with Load More pagination, server-
  side type filtering, client-side search on loaded items only
- bookmarks/todos/learn pages: unwrap .items from new response shape

Default page sizes: notes 30, bookmarks 30, todos 50, learningNotes 30.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
